headline: Evercore ISI sees Humana on path to margin recovery
summary: Investing.com -- Evercore ISI initiated coverage of Humana with an In Line rating and a $295 price target on Monday, highlighting both medium-term uncertainties and long-term earnings growth potential.

headline: Assessing Humana (HUM): Is the Current Share Price a True Bargain?
summary: Humana (HUM) has been on investors’ radars lately, and even though there isn’t a single headline-grabbing event behind its recent moves, the stock’s trajectory itself is raising a lot of questions. For investors trying to decide whether now is the moment to step in or stay on the sidelines, this kind of price action, absent a clear external catalyst, can be telling.
